ss.  And while I (and I assume many others) am able to see the beauty inherent within every person, I’d venture to guess that most of us don’t view ourselves that way.</p>\n\n<p>An 18-year-old student from Chicago embarked on a high school project that would quickly become much larger than she had anticipated.  <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/gloverfull/">Shea Glover</a></strong> invited students and teachers to pose for portraits; some of whom she knew, some of whom were total strangers.</p>\n\n<p>As these people were standing in front of her camera, she would tell them the purpose of the project: “I’m taking pictures of things I find beautiful.”</p>\n\n<p>The following video documented the beautiful, raw emotion that is expressed when people are caught a tiny bit off guard by being told they’re beautiful.  It is truly amazing the power that one word holds.  Watch and remember that you are just as beautiful as the next person, in your own, unique, perfect way.</p>\n\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="658" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aW8BDgLpZkI?feature=oembed" width="1170"></iframe>\n\n<div class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1310px">![](http://images5.aplus.com/uc-up/411f2a0a-dede-475d-b91e-2e1656778695/411f2a0a-dede-475d-b91e-2e1656778695.inline_yes)**Photo credit: Shea Glover**\n\n</div><div class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1310px">![](http://images5.aplus.com/uc-up/f84b813f-0302-4e9d-8fd7-7703be11767f/f84b813f-0302-4e9d-8fd7-7703be11767f.inline_yes)**Photo credit: Shea Glover**\n\n</div><div class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1310px">![](http://images5.aplus.com/uc-up/2097d008-801d-4324-8c4c-72b0e539c6bf/2097d008-801d-4324-8c4c-72b0e539c6bf.inline_yes)**Photo credit: Shea Glover**\n\n</div><div class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1310px">![](http://images5.aplus.com/uc-up/3585ee7a-99d2-41fb-97a6-eb6f0d9d0145/3585ee7a-99d2-41fb-97a6-eb6f0d9d0145.inline_yes)**Photo credit: Shea Glover**\n\n</div><