le to find them.  Love makes the Leo act the most crazy, turning the King of the Jungle into an insecure, mess of a person.  Leos, you just need to accept what is happening in your life, and let it be.</span>\n\n**Virgo**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Virgos, in order to reduce the stress in your life, you need to stop thinking so much.  Don’t be afraid to try new things, even though the thought of stepping out of the comfort zone can be terrifying.  Visualize yourself overcoming the obstacles in your life, trust that you’re in the right place and stay positive.</span>\n\n**Libra**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Libras value fairness quite a bit, so when they feel they’re getting the short end of the stick, they’re not at all happy about it.  If you want to confront someone, do it in a calm and composed manner, don’t let yourself brood for days and then blow up on someone.  Keep it sweet and to the point, let people know what your stance is on the matter.</span>\n\n**Scorpio**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Scorpio is a sensitive being, but they are able to hide it well.  The Scorpio’s strength is subtle, meaning you’re not a fan of loudness or noise and you enjoy having privacy.  Allow people to know your boundaries and needs so that a winning solution for everyone can be reached.</span>\n\n**Sagittarius**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Sagittarius hates stagnation, so you’re prone to absolutely hating traffic.  You don’t enjoy any activities where you have to be on your best behavior to please someone else.  Stress in your life derives mainly from work or your partner as they seemingly demand things from your constantly.  Take the time to be outside, so as to free your restless spirit every now and then.</span>\n\n**Capricorn**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Capricorn sets high expectations for itself, and you feel pressure to succeed when you fail to reach your goals.  Never waste your time in self-loathing or deep contemplation a