1347	ef472d74-3bd5-4771-a91d-4e686e3ee020	5 Great Alternatives to Wearing a Bra	5-great-alternatives-to-wearing-a-bra	\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">While recent movements like #[FreeTheNipple](http://freethenipple.com/) and #[NoBraDay](https://www.awarenessdays.co.uk/awareness-days-calendar/national-no-bra-day/) are meant to empower women all over the world, it turns out that a lot of women actually </span>*<span style="font-weight: 400;">like</span>*<span style="font-weight: 400;"> the function and purpose of the bra.  </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">While most of us are for women gaining equality on the topless front, and [there’s even been some research into why you shouldn’t even be wearing a bra](http://www.iflscience.com/health-and-medicine/no-bra-day-special-are-bras-bad-you), a lot of women feel that going without one is impractical.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Women use bras for all sorts of different reasons, from simply keeping them stationary to relieving back pressure to hiding the occasional erect nipple.  </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re looking to try out something new, something different from your standard bra, check out these five great alternatives:</span>\n\n**The Pasty!**![seashell pasties](http://rack.1.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE1LzEwLzEzLzZlL3NlYXNoZWxscGFzLmE4MmRiLmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTEyMDB4OTYwMD4/4688dd5e/aa8/seashell-pasties.jpg "seashell pasties")\n\n![MTV Video Music Awards At The Metropolitan Opera House At Lincoln Center](http://rack.0.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE1LzEwLzEzL2I4L2xpbGtpbTEuNDA0ODYuanBnCnAJdGh1bWIJMTIwMHg5NjAwPg/356039d9/f48/lil-kim1.jpg "MTV Video Music Awards At The Metropolitan Opera House At Lincoln Center")\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Maybe you want the coverage on your nipples, but also like to feel free and uninhibited.  Pasties come in a variety of different designs, shapes and colors, and use a light adhesive to keep them in place.  They’re also quite festive, meanin