n</ul>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">These are all traits that describe a person with a strong empathic affinity.  </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Now, a few methods and tips for managing your gift, so that you might not feel so exhausted and overwhelmed by the energies you face on a day-to-day basis:</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Certain crystals hold energy-deflecting properties.  Try wearing jet, black tourmaline, hematite, or tiger’s eye on the right side of your body.  These help push energy outward, helping you create a protective barrier around yourself.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bathing in salts, like pink Himalayan salt, does wonders</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Develop a way to shield your solar plexus using your hands and arms while visualizing the act as well</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Burn sage in and around yourself and the spaces you occupy</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Practice saying “no” to people–Be honest and open when you tell them that you simply don’t have the time or cannot assist them at the moment.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ask for energetic protection from your spiritual guides, angels, and other non-physical helpers</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-weight: 400;">Saying phrases aloud that help you to visualize being protected like: “I am creating a bubble around myself for protection today,” or, “My shields are up now.”</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Hopefully some of these suggestions can help your empathic side exist happily and harmoniously with the rest of the world.  Be social and confident knowing that you no longer have to hide from overwhelming situations.  </span></p>\n\n<p>h/t <a href="http://themysticalmoon.blogspot.com/2014/09/how-to-cope-as-empath-in-our-society.html"><strong>Mystical Moon</strong></a></p>	http://cdn.heartcenteredrebalancing.c