1351	9bd06240-e431-4b1e-931b-fae11671080e	You've Been Using Post-It Notes Incorrectly This Entire Time	youve-been-using-post-it-notes-incorrectly-this-entire-time	\nWhile Post-It Notes do not require a great deal of intellect to use, most people have been using them all wrong for as long as they’ve been alive.\n\n![You've Definitely Been Using Post-Its Wrong Your Entire Life](http://thumbs.mic.com/NjliMTQ3MDNiOCMvYURscUV2YjdoYmZiNmZzNy1JdDFQdWZibERZPS8yMHgwOjc4MHgyNjQvNzYweDI2NC9maWx0ZXJzOnF1YWxpdHkoNzApL2h0dHA6Ly9zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tL3BvbGljeW1pYy1pbWFnZXMvY2ZtenJuYjhkaWZyaW5ldzB4c3RkcGxva2dyY2plMjg2em1waGpwazVvdXZ6emdycGoxcDljZm1wcmV4MnZwYy5qcGc.jpg)\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Typically, when you go to unstick a new post-it note, you grab from the bottom and peel upward, yes?  And you usually get a bent-out-of-shape note that rarely hangs flat on the surface that you stick it to, yes?  Well here’s the solution to the air pocket that sits between the note and the surface!</span>\n\n**Peel each note from the side, just underneath the sticky part**\n\n![You've Definitely Been Using Post-Its Wrong Your Entire Life](http://thumbs.mic.com/NzZjYWY3OGY4OCMvNzlsNUVyRXZudkk2UGpzaFhyX0plLWJCRWYwPS8yMHgwOjc4MHgyNjQvNzYweDI2NC9maWx0ZXJzOnF1YWxpdHkoNzApL2h0dHA6Ly9zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tL3BvbGljeW1pYy1pbWFnZXMvbW5vamtubXV4cjRtMmZtdGloYWlteXp2MHp4emo0YThzbWJsNW01cmI3ZmIwdW13NW84YnRka2xlcGlrMWJldS5qcGc.jpg)\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">This technique will give you a note that rests perfectly flat on the surface, just like you wanted in the first place.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">This tutorial and life-changing tip was highlighted by blogger **[Martin Schapendonk](http://blog.whitehorses.nl/2013/05/17/how-to-stick-a-sticky-note/)**.</span>\n\n\n	\N	<p>While Post-It Notes do not require a great deal of intellect to use, most people have been using them all wrong for as long as they’ve been alive.</p>\n\n<p><img src="http://thumbs.mic.com/NjliMTQ3MDNiOCMvY