1440	db91bfad-093a-4e77-b6af-77ddc95db657	Dealing With Heartbreak Using Your Zodiac Sign	dealing-with-heartbreak-using-your-zodiac-sign	\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re going through a tough time and have had to separate from your partner recently, you might be left feeling lost and confused.  Heartbreak affects everyone differently, and your zodiac sign has a lot to do with that.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Here’s a bit of insight as to how each sign handles the pain of heartbreak, so that you might grow a little easier:</span>\n\n**Aquarius**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Getting close to people is difficult for you, so when you do fall, you fall hard; which makes breaking up that much harder.  You’re not one to outwardly express the pain you’re feeling because you don’t like feeling vulnerable, so you stay busy and speak only to those who are close to you.</span>\n\n**Pisces**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">You’re likely to fully embrace the sadness and sorrow accompanied with most breakups, but you do so because you are not worried about being vulnerable or showing ‘weakness.’  You know that to fully heal you must finish your grieving.</span>\n\n**Aries**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">When the Aries gets hurt, they tend to look to their friends for support because of how social and outgoing they are.  Aries like to stay busy when they’re hurting; this lets them cover their pain with work and activities, pretending as if it hasn’t phased them.</span>\n\n**Taurus**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Taurus struggles at times to adequately express how they’re feeling and what they’re thinking.  You’re quick to be set off as you occasionally let your emotions flare up, but you have only kindness in your heart, and want someone who loves as deeply as you do.</span>\n\n**Gemini**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Gemini tend to live in the moment, so a failed relationship or parting of ways is simply water under the bridge. 