1490	08ef2522-9e50-4ec8-824c-757d62ba6cb2	How To Find Love Based on Your Zodiac Sign	how-to-find-love-based-on-your-zodiac-sign	\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Falling in love is different for everyone, and our zodiac signs have a lot to do with how it happens. It makes sense though, doesn’t it? The universe will always influence who we are as people. Just as the Cancer will always be loving and caring, and the Leo proud and passionate.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’re looking to find love, learning a bit about what your sign desires in a partner might just be the difference between a lasting, loving relationship, and a drama-filled nightmare.</span>\n\n\n## **Aries (March 21-April 19)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">As a youthful fire sign, Aries have a fervent energy and enthusiasm for life. Your leadership skills often let you control the flow of any relationship, which is good because you’re usually the one who is down-to-earth and level-headed. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Try not to put the cart before the horse, and people will flock to your ever burning flame.</span>\n\n\n## **Taurus (April 20-May 20)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Taurus have a weak spot for physical intimacy. When the physical side of a relationship picks up heavy and fast, you’re likely to start falling in love at the same time. This is largely because of how in tune you are sensually with your body.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">When you do find yourself in a faithful relationship, you’re happy just ebbing and flowing within it. Which is why your dream is to settle down together somewhere remote and secluded.</span>\n\n\n## **Gemini (May 21-June 20)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Smart, funny and always looking on the bright side, Gemini always make great partners. They’re full of unique and intelligent ideas. They’re also incredibly romantic, which means they often fall in love and stay in love when they adore their partner. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">While you might want nothing more than to be with your significant other 24/7, it is good to remember to give each other space, and to communicate with each other as much as possible.</span>\n\n\n## **Cancer (June 21-July 22)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">While Cancers tend to fall face first into love (and hard), they keep a bit of reserved skepticism. You’re searching for someone who will be your ‘partner,’ in every sense of the word. Which is why they prefer partners who are ambitious and motivated.</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you’ve found a partner, you’re their number one fan. And your superb listening skills and sense of humor will keep them around for years to come.</span>\n\n\n## **Leo (July 23-August 22)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Because Leos are so charismatic, confident and warm, they rarely struggle to find love. But there natural ability to attract others doesn’t keep them from being completely loyal once they’ve fallen for someone. And they tend to fall in love often, and hard. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">As a Leo, you are naturally territorial, but it’s only because of how intense your love is. You need a bit of praise and adoration here and there to keep you happy.</span>\n\n\n## **Virgo (August 23-September 22)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Virgos sometimes forget just how easy to love they really are. And they don’t like to show any sort of vulnerability. These two notions combined mean that they typically prefer to operate under jealousy and accusations, rather than playing it cool like they so often want to do. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Don’t let yourself become consumed by the idea of love. You need to give people the chance to love you.</span>\n\n\n## **Libra (September 23-October 22)**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Libras are naturally independent and ambitious, which means that love is just another thing in this world 