/p>\n\n<h2 id="ariesmarch21april19"><strong>Aries (March 21-April 19)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As a youthful fire sign, Aries have a fervent energy and enthusiasm for life. Your leadership skills often let you control the flow of any relationship, which is good because you’re usually the one who is down-to-earth and level-headed. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Try not to put the cart before the horse, and people will flock to your ever burning flame.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="taurusapril20may20"><strong>Taurus (April 20-May 20)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Taurus have a weak spot for physical intimacy. When the physical side of a relationship picks up heavy and fast, you’re likely to start falling in love at the same time. This is largely because of how in tune you are sensually with your body.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When you do find yourself in a faithful relationship, you’re happy just ebbing and flowing within it. Which is why your dream is to settle down together somewhere remote and secluded.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="geminimay21june20"><strong>Gemini (May 21-June 20)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Smart, funny and always looking on the bright side, Gemini always make great partners. They’re full of unique and intelligent ideas. They’re also incredibly romantic, which means they often fall in love and stay in love when they adore their partner. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">While you might want nothing more than to be with your significant other 24/7, it is good to remember to give each other space, and to communicate with each other as much as possible.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="cancerjune21july22"><strong>Cancer (June 21-July 22)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">While Cancers tend to fall face first into love (and hard), they keep a bit of reserved skepticism. You’re searching for someone who will be your ‘partner,’ in every sense of the word. Which is why they prefer partners who are ambitious and motivated.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you’ve found a partner, you’re their number one fan. And your superb listening skills and sense of humor will keep them around for years to come.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="leojuly23august22"><strong>Leo (July 23-August 22)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Because Leos are so charismatic, confident and warm, they rarely struggle to find love. But there natural ability to attract others doesn’t keep them from being completely loyal once they’ve fallen for someone. And they tend to fall in love often, and hard. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As a Leo, you are naturally territorial, but it’s only because of how intense your love is. You need a bit of praise and adoration here and there to keep you happy.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="virgoaugust23september22"><strong>Virgo (August 23-September 22)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Virgos sometimes forget just how easy to love they really are. And they don’t like to show any sort of vulnerability. These two notions combined mean that they typically prefer to operate under jealousy and accusations, rather than playing it cool like they so often want to do. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Don’t let yourself become consumed by the idea of love. You need to give people the chance to love you.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="libraseptember23october22"><strong>Libra (September 23-October 22)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Libras are naturally independent and ambitious, which means that love is just another thing in this world that they can choose to pursue, or not pursue. This also means that when they do pick a partner, they’re nothing short of the high standards that have been set. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your high levels of self-respect often have you forcing partners to wait some time before you actually commit to anything.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once you’ve found love, your focus will shift toward stability within the relationship.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="scorpiooctober23november21"><strong>Scorpio (October 23-November 21)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whoa, watch out, the Scorpio is coming through. Passionate, sexual, stubborn and intense, the Scorpio likes to follow the heart, rather than the brain. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Love is highly valued by Scorpios, and they’re used to getting their way, so their relationships often include a good bit of drama. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Calm and rational partners are perfect for the Scorpio; you fit best with Pisces or Cancer.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="sagittariusnovember22december21"><strong>Sagittarius (November 22-December 21)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As the ultimate free-spirit, Sagittarius like to treat love like a journey, one that they’re not afraid to embark on. When it comes to matters of the heart, you enjoy throwing inhibition to the wind, jumping head-first into love.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Fortunately, your intellectual nature attracts similar-minded partners, ones that share your enthusiasm for novelty experiences and seeing the world.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Just as you want, you will likely find a partner who’s just as afraid of settling down as you are.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="capricorndecember22january19"><strong>Capricorn (December 22-January 19)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Capricorns like having something to work on. This is easy for them when it comes to relationships because they’re really good at seeing big-picture type of stuff. A happy, stable life with the person that they love and call their best friend is something to work toward. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’re quite serious when it comes to life, so you expect your partner to be as well. Reckless, crazy passion has no place in your world.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="aquariusjanuary20february18"><strong>Aquarius (January 20-February 18)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Aquarius, your big heart often reflects the type of love you desire most: passionate, intense, hot and long-lasting. If you find yourself in love with someone, don’t be afraid to be the selfless person you are. Enjoy devoting time and energy to your relationship without playing games.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’ll know when you’ve found the right person, because you’ll never want to let go once you do.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id="piscesfebruary19march20"><strong>Pisces (February 19-March 20)</strong></h2>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pisces, one of the things you fear most is missing out on your chance to fall in love. You’re highly sensitive, which means your moods can be somewhat polarized at times. Good things in your relationship have you feeling happy, euphoric and carefree, while the bad things often ruin your entire day.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your naturally sweet and caring nature is redeeming, however, as you often put your partner’s needs before your own. Just remember not to sacrifice too much of your own life for the sake of theirs.</span></p>\n\n<p>h/t <a href="http://elitedaily.com/dating/zodiac-sign-says-love/1267932/"><strong>EliteDaily</strong></a></p>	http://cdn.heartcenteredrebalancing.com/2016/08/feature_image_lovetemplate.jpg	f	f	published	en_US	public	\N	\N	1	2016-08-05 07:40:37+00	1	2016-08-05 07:40:37+00	1	2016-08-05 07:40:37+00	1
