ble of achieving their goals and that you’ll be by their side every step of the way.</span></p>\n\n<p><strong>‘I’m committed to you, to us’</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Knowing that your partner is entirely faithful and committed to the love you two share is an amazing feeling.  Never hesitate to tell them that your heart is theirs or how often you think about them.  </span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The open expression of commitment illustrates your love and sincerity for this feeling toward them.  When you’re feeling the love, tell them!</span></p>\n\n<p>h/t <a href="http://www.relrules.com/9-phrases-more-important-than-i-love-you/5/"><strong>ReRules</strong></a></p>	http://cdn.heartcenteredrebalancing.com/2016/06/feature_ima545454ge_template.jpg	f	f	published	en_US	public	\N	\N	1	2016-06-30 08:13:16+00	1	2016-06-30 08:13:16+00	1	2016-06-30 08:13:16+00	1
