1501	b4b68601-5702-44f7-9e3f-4dedaadee281	10 Signs Your Better Half is the Best Partner For You	10-signs-your-better-half-is-the-best-partner-for-you	\n<iframe allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" class="rumble" frameborder="0" height="360" src="https://rumble.com/embed/u7jac.vd8q8/" width="640"></iframe>\n\n**They know you better than you do**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Your better half is perfect for you when they know you just as well as you know yourself. They know what you’re thinking, your attitudes toward certain things, and enjoy being there for you during moments of weakness.</span>\n\n**They love to make you smile and laugh**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">A perfect partner loves to see their significant other smile and be as happy as possible. If your partner’s sense of humor is something you adore, you’ll never tire of them.</span>\n\n**They’re there for you, even when you’re grumpy**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">A perfect partner recognizes when their significant other is upset, irritated or frustrated, and doesn’t get down about it. They know that you have your angry moments just like everyone else. They’re not about to let those moments keep them from loving you, they know to just give you space every now and then.</span>\n\n**They’re not judgmental of your choices when it comes to their appearance**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">A great spouse always supports their partner, especially when it comes to them wanting to look better or feel more attractive. However you want to present yourself to the world, they love you for it.</span>\n\n**They’ll always be upfront with you**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">A great partner will never beat around the bush or lie to you. They will always give you their honest opinion because they always have your best interests in mind. </span>\n\n**They’re good at righting any wrongs, even if it’s not immediate**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Everyone makes mistakes, and a good partner knows this. If they’ve done something to upset you or frustrate you, they know that they’ll make it up to you in one way or another. Just give them some time; they always figure it out.</span>\n\n**They understand that special moments together will always trump any sort of material possession**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">A good partner would rather do something with his or her significant other that will create lasting memories for both of you. Buying someone luxurious and expensive things is nice, but those things will never be able to match the feelings you have when you and your partner experience something together.</span>\n\n**They give your family the same respect they give their own**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">When your better half respects and treats your family as if they were their own, you know you’ve found a keeper. Family time is always better when everyone loves and respects each other.</span>\n\n**They truly listen, and care about what’s going on in your life**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Something that truly makes a partner great is how good they are at listening to you. If they’re genuinely concerned with how your day is going and want to fix anything wrong in your life, they’re perfect for you.</span>\n\n**They enjoy showing how much they appreciate you in different ways**\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Sometimes saying “I love you” just doesn’t adequately describe how much you care for a person. The perfect partner loves expressing his or her gratitude for everything you do to make their life better. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">From little things like making them coffee in the mornings, to big things like supporting their goals and ambitions.</span>\n\n\n	\N	<iframe allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" class="rumble" frameborder="0" height="360" src="https://rumble.com/embed/u7jac.vd8q8/" width="640"></iframe>\n\n<p><strong>They know you better than you do</strong></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your bet